Titolo: Everybody's Gone to the Rapture

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Everybody's Gone to the Rapture is a 2015 adventure game developed by The Chinese Room. It is a story-based game, taking place in a small English village whose inhabitants have mysteriously disappeared. It is considered a spiritual successor to Dear Esther, also by The Chinese Room. It was published by Sony Computer Entertainment and released for the PlayStation 4 on 11 August 2015. It was released for Windows on 14 April 2016.